  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Packing / East / 5 Days / E-commerce)",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Basic UP$2800 + OT</strong></p><p><strong>• Working location at Macpherson  </strong></p><p><strong>• Working hours: 9am – 6pm (Monday – Friday) </strong></p><p><strong>• AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></p><p><strong>• Well Established Ecommerce Company </strong><br /></p><p></p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Picking and packing of items for shipments (items are lightweight, each less than 0.5kg)</li><li>Handle incoming shipments. </li><li>Counting and checking of items.</li><li>Printing of shipment labels</li><li>Handing over the packages to couriers like DHL, FedEx etc. for delivery to customers</li><li>Manage warehouse space</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>O Level and above </li><li>1 – 3 years of relevant work experience</li></ul><p></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:<br /></p><p></p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br /></p><p>KHOO SOT MEI (R21102604)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
